Resource Profile: AT IPS Patient

Official URL: https://fhir.hl7.at/elga-austrianpatientsummary-r4/StructureDefinition/at-ips-patient Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2024-05-27 Computable Name: AtIpsPatient

This AT IPS profile for the Patient resource is derived from the corresponding HL7® Austria FHIR® Core profile and also ensures IPS conformity via the IPS profile referenced by the so-called imposeProfile extension.
